    <note>Mosi(1) Xie [1373] A client of Qin(1) Gui [8008]. Hu's [1374] younger brother. Xie's great grandson, Shaozhi [3680], was a Suzhou juren in 1234. Wang(2) Zhidao's [1786] son-in-law, Mosi(1) Kan [3679], was Xie's grandson. His son-in-law, Wu(3) Quan [4006], was a Jianning, Pucheng resident, who used his grandfather's yin to enter the civil service. Jiangsu jin, 11.11b; XNYL, 75.8b, 136.15a, 17b, 176.12b; SS, 474.1b-2a; Suzhou FZ, 139.23a; Sun Di, Daquan ji, 61.1a; Sun Di, WJ, 36.1a. CBD, 1, 21-22.</note>
